title: East Austin - Studio
posting_body: Brand new community nearby Houndstooth Coffee and more popping up soon.
Very quick walk to the MLK Train station will get you to downtown in minutes or head up north towards the domain.
Be the first to live in this community!
Units are priced below other complexes in the area.
Luxurious amenities are found throughout the property, which include a swimming pool and fitness center.
This is a pet friendly property!
I am a Realtor/apartment locator in the Austin area.
My services are 100% free, don’t hesitate to give me a call.
If you'd like to learn more about this property, or would like to review other available options, call/text or email me.
